d%2080-90%20Tests%20(84).%20Consistency%20has%20been%20an%20issue%2C%20he%20will%20have%20to%20overcome%20it%20because%20India%20have%20a%20good%20captaincy%20option%20in%20him%20after%20Rohit%20Sharma%20is%20done.%20Rahane%20will%20have%20to%20make%20runs%2C%20and%20then%20everything%20else%20will%20follow%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaffer%20said%20on%20Jio%20Cinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaffer%20also%20stated%20that%20Rahane%20could%20have%20become%20India's%20Test%20captain%20after%202-1%20win%20over%20Australia%20in%20the%202021%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20his%20form%20was%20great%20from%20that%20Australia%20series%20after%20that%2036%20all%20out%2C%20the%20way%20he%20led%2C%20scored%20a%20hundred%20in%20Melbourne...%20had%20his%20form%20remained%20the%20same%2C%20he%20would%20have%20been%20the%20next%20Test%20captain.%20But%20he%20lost%20his%20form%20and%20got%20dropped%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20India%20batter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20he%20reinvented%20himself%20in%20the%20IPL%20and%20got%20a%20chance%20in%20the%20WTC%20final.%20He%20was%20appointed%20the%20vice-captain%20as%20well%2C%20because%20the%20Indian%20selectors%20see%20a%20good%20leader%20in%20him.%20He%20still%20has%20age%20on%20his%20side%20but%20he%20needs%20to%20score%20runs%2C%20if%20he%20does%20not%20then%20he%20will%20find%20it%20difficult%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690042620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2F4ge4d5cg_wasim-jaffer_625x300_21_June_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fgood-captaincy-option-after-rohit-sharma-wasim-jaffer-backs-this-player-to-lead-team-india-in-future-4232172%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wasim%20Jaffer%20said%20that%20the%20player%20needs%20to%20score%20runs%20consistently%20in%20order%20to%20become%20India%20captain%20after%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20reign.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%