o%20Vietnam%20People's%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Navy%20said%20the%20ship%20has%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20Vietnam%20People's%20Navy%20(VPN)%20with%20complete%20%26quot%3Bweapon%20complement%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday's%20handing-over%20ceremony%20symbolises%20the%20deep-rooted%20friendship%20and%20strategic%20partnership%20between%20India%20and%20Vietnam%2C%26quot%3B%20Admiral%20Kumar%20said%20in%20his%20address%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20makes%20this%20occasion%20even%20more%20significant%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20this%20is%20the%20first-ever%20occasion%20that%20India%20is%20offering%20a%20fully-operational%20Corvette%20to%20any%20friendly%20foreign%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%20Chief%20said%20the%20transfer%20of%20INS%20Kirpan%20to%20the%20Vietnam%20People's%20Navy%20resonates%20with%20India's%20G20%20vision%20of%20%26quot%3BVasudhaiva%20Kutumbakam%20---%20One%20Earth%2C%20One%20Family%2C%20One%20Future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVietnam%2C%20an%20important%20ASEAN%20(Association%20of%20Southeast%20Asian%20Nations)%20country%2C%20has%20territorial%20disputes%20with%20China%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20oil%20exploration%20projects%20in%20the%20Vietnamese%20waters%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea.%20India%20and%20Vietnam%20have%20been%20boosting%20their%20maritime%20security%20cooperation%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20to%20protect%20common%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday's%20event%20serves%20as%20a%20reaffirmation%20of%20our%20commitment%20to%20expand%20and%20deepen%20our%20defence%20partnership%2C%20not%20only%20bilaterally%20but%20also%20in%20the%20broader%20multilateral%20framework%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdmiral%20Kumar%20hoped%20that%20INS%20Kirpan%20would%20continue%20to%20navigate%20the%20vast%20seas%2C%20%26quot%3Bupholding%20the%20principles%20of%20freedom%2C%20justice%2C%20and%20international%20rules-based%20order%20to%20be%20the%20pillar%20around%20which%20a%20'force%20for%20good'%20be%20built%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20comments%20come%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20China's%20increasing%20military%20muscle%20flexing%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20entrust%20INS%20Kirpan%20to%20the%20Vietnam%20Navy%2C%20we%20do%20so%20with%20complete%20confidence%20in%20their%20ability%20to%20operate%20and%20maintain%20this%20magnificent%20vessel%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Navy%20Chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20certain%20that%20they%20will%20harness%20its%20immense%20potential%20to%20safeguard%20their%20national%20maritime%20interests%2C%20contribute%20to%20regional%20security%2C%20and%20foster%20peace%20and%20stability%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINS%20Kirpan%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20Vietnam%20after%20it%20was%20decommissioned%20from%20Indian%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20completing%2032%20years%20of%20illustrious%20service%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20Indian%20naval%20ship%20Kirpan%20has%20been%20decommissioned%20from%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20and%20handed%20over%20to%20VPN%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINS%20Kirpan%2C%20since%20its%20commissioning%20in%201991%2C%20has%20been%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20Indian%20Navy's%20Eastern%20Fleet%20and%20has%20participated%20in%20many%20operations%20over%20the%20last%2032%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManned%20by%20about%2012%20officers%20and%20100%20sailors%2C%20the%20ship%20is%2090%20metres%20long%20and%2010.45%20metres%20in%20width%20with%20maximum%20displacement%20of%201%2C450%20tons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20transfer%20of%20INS%20Kirpan%20from%20Indian%20Navy%20to%20Vietnam%20People's%20Navy%2C%20symbolises%20the%20status%20of%20Indian%20Navy%20of%20being%20the%20'preferred%20security%20partner%20in%20%C2%A0the%20Ind