%20illegal%20for%20US%20poultry%20plants%20to%20hire%20minors.%20The%20company%20says%20a%20hiring%20agency%20misled%20them%20about%20his%20age.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPerez%20is%20the%20third%20minor%20in%20the%20last%20month%20to%20die%20in%20a%20US%20workplace%2C%20the%20Huffington%20Post%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDuvan%20Tomas%20Perez%20was%20just%2010%20years%20old%20when%20he%20moved%20from%20Guatemala%20to%20the%20United%20States%20with%20his%20family.%20Now%2C%20six%20years%20later%2C%20he%20is%20dead%20because%20of%20a%20workplace%20accident%20at%20a%20poultry%20plant%20that%20should've%20never%20hired%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerez%2C%2016%2C%20died%20on%20July%2014%20at%20the%20Mar-Jac%20poultry%20plant%20in%20Hattiesburg%2C%20Mississippi%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2F16-year-old-boy-dies-accident-mississippi-poultry-plant-rcna94963%5C%22%3ENBC%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%20He%20died%20from%20his%20injuries%20after%20becoming%20trapped%20in%20equipment%20on%20a%20conveyor%20belt.%20It%20is%20illegal%20under%20federal%20law%20for%20minors%20to%20work%20in%20poultry%20plants%20due%20to%20the%20inherent%20workplace%20safety%20hazards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Mar-Jac%20Poultry%20plant%20in%20Hattiesburg%2C%20Mississippi%20claims%20an%20outside%20hiring%20agency%20misled%20the%20company%20by%20misrepresenting%20the%20boy's%20age%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fteen-poultry-factory-child-worker-deaths_n_64b7ecbce4b0ad7b75f67af7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Huffington%20Post%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHiring%20agencies%20are%20often%20unreliable%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20ensuring%20workers%20are%20not%20minors%20and%20have%20the%20proper%20qualifications%20for%20hazardous%20workplaces%2C%20Jordan%20Barab%2C%20former%20deputy%20assistant%20secretary%20of%20labor%20at%20the%20Occupational%20Safety%