%20Koushal%20Kumar%2C%20superintendent%20of%20Kathua%20district%20jail%2C%20who%20is%20also%20in-charge%20of%20the%20holding%20centre%2C%20the%20baby%20was%20suffering%20from%20some%20ailment%20and%20died%20two%20days%20after%20the%20incident%20at%20the%20detention%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20filed%20an%20FIR%20against%20Rohingyas%20allegedly%20involved%20in%20stone%20pelting%20at%20Hiranagar%20sub-jail%20-%20designated%20as%20the%20holding%20centre%20for%20Rohingyas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E271%20Rohingyas%2C%20among%20them%20144%20women%20and%20children%20are%20detained%20at%20the%20holding%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClashes%20broke%20out%20after%20Rohingyas%2C%20who%20held%20multiple%20hunger%20strike%20protests%20in%20the%20holding%20centre%2C%20demanded%20their%20release%20and%20deportation%20to%20their%20native%20country%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20resorted%20to%20lathicharge%20and%20resorted%20tear-gas%20shelling%20as%20a%20control%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20said%20the%20police%20were%20compelled%20to%20take%20action%20after%20inmates%20took%20three%20officials%20of%20jail%20staff%2C%20including%20a%20special%20police%20official%2C%20hostage%20and%20tried%20to%20break%20open%20the%20gate%20of%20the%20sub-jail%20at%20Hiranagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRohingyas%20have%20been%20demanding%20their%20release%20and%20deportation%20to%20their%20native%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20said%20they%20have%20already%20forwarded%20the%20case%20to%20the%20home%20department%20for%20the%20deportation%20of%20Rohingyas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalim%20Mohammad%20and%20his%20wife%20had%20come%20to%20Jammu%20in%202012.%20The%20couple%2C%20along%20with%20their%20eldest%20son%2C%20were%20arrested%20by%20police%20during%20the%20checking%20of%20refugee%20cards%20issued%20by%20the%20UN.%20Even%20as%20Salim%20also%20had%20a%20UNHCR%20card%20that%20allows%20Rohingyas%20to%20stay%20as%20refugees%2C%20the%20family%20was%20lodged%20at%20the%20Jammu%20district%20jail%20at%20Ambphalla%20before%20they%20were%20shifted%20to%20the%20holding%20centre%20in%20Hiranagar%20in%202021.%20The%20couple%20then%20went%20on%20to%20have%20two%20more%20children%20at%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20several%20years%2C%20political%20parties%20and%20right-wing%20groups%20have%20been%20demanding%20the%20deportation%20of%20Rohingya%20refugee%20from%20Jammu.%20These%20groups%20allege%20that%20Rohingyas%20have%20been%20settled%20in%20Jammu%20as%20a%20part%20of%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20engineer%20a%20demographic%20change%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20these%20years%2C%20hundreds%20of%20shanties%20and%20hutments%20of%20the%20Rohingyas%20were%20burnt%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690039380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F3fi25avo_parents-in-handcuff-at-babys-funeral-ndtv_625x300_22_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frohingya-couple-attends-babys-burial-in-handcuffs-in-jammu-and-kashmir-4232528%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Rohingya%20couple%20was%20brought%20in%20handcuffs%20for%20the%20last%20rites%20of%20their%20child%20who%20died%20in%20a%20refugee%20detention%20centre%20near%20Jammu.%20A%20video%20of%20the%20handcuffed%20parents%20at%20the%20burial%20site%20has%20been%20widely%20shared%20on%20social%20media.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frohingya-couple-attends-babys-burial-in-handcuffs-in-jammu-and-kashmir-4232528%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frohingya-couple-attends-babys-burial-in-handcuffs-in-jammu-and-kashmir-4232528%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frohingya-couple-attends-babys-burial-in-handcuffs-in-jammu-and-kashmir-4232528%