%2Fon-day-of-manipur-mob-horror-2-gang-raped-killed-40km-away%2Farticleshow%2F102024469.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20male%20friend%20of%20the%20women%2C%20who%20saw%20an%20ambulance%20pick%20them%20up%2C%20reached%20the%20hospital%20the%20next%20day%20and%20was%20told%20they%20had%20succumbed%20to%20the%20injuries.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20dragged%20one%20of%20them%20inside%2C%20switched%20off%20the%20lights%2C%20and%20took%20turns%20raping%20her.%20Then%20they%20did%20the%20same%20to%20my%20other%20co-worker.%20They%20gagged%20both%20with%20clothes%20to%20prevent%20them%20from%20screaming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20women%20in%20that%20particular%20mob%20encouraged%20men%20to%20take%20the%20women%20into%20a%20room%20and%20assault%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20about%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%2C%20the%20women%20were%20dragged%20out%20of%20the%20room%20and%20were%20dumped%20near%20a%20sawmill%20in%20the%20vicinity.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20clothes%20were%20torn%2C%20their%20hair%20chopped%20off%2C%20and%20their%20bodies%20covered%20in%20blood%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20man%2C%20also%20a%20tribal%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20conveyed%20the%20information%20to%20a%20cousin%20of%20one%20of%20the%20women%20who%20was%20hiding%20in%20a%20church%20to%20escape%20the%20clashes%20outside.%20It%20was%20only%20when%20the%20cousin%20in%20question%20was%20evacuated%20to%20Kangpokpi%20by%20Assam%20Rifles%20the%20families%20of%20the%20women%20got%20to%20know%20of%20what%20had%20happened%20to%20their%20daughters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20earlier%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-imphal-violence-daughters-killed%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20a%20detailed%20account%20by%20the%20fathers%20of%20the%20women%20%E2%80%93%20the%20women%20were%20aged%2021%20and%2024.%20The%20report%20was%20published%20on%20May%2029%2C%20giving%20a%20blow-by-blow%20account%20of%20how%20the%20crime%20unfolded%20and%20what%20happened%20next.%20One%20of%20the%20fathers%20had%20then%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20might%20have%20been%20sexually%20abused%20too%2C%20though%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20say%20it%20for%20sure%20yet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20a%20suo%20muto%20FIR%20was%20registered%20at%20Porompat%20police%20station%20in%20Imphal%20East%20district.%20Later%2C%20the%20mother%20of%20one%20of%20the%20two%20women%2C%20after%20much%20hesitation%2C%20filed%20a%20zero%20FIR%20at%20Saikul%20police%20station%20on%20May%2016.%20Zero%20FIRs%20are%20filed%20at%20any%20police%20station%20irrespective%20of%20jurisdiction.%20The%20FIR%20was%20then%20transferred%20to%20the%20Porompat%20police%20station%20on%20June%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20family%20member%20of%20one%20of%20the%20women%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fin-manipur-another-fir-on-rape-murder-of-2-young-women-family-in-dark-about-probe-8853540%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20still%20haven%E2%80%99t%20received%20any%20post-mortem%20report%20from%20the%20police%20although%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20more%20than%20a%20month%20since%20the%20FIR%20was%20filed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWoman%20set%20ablaze%20by%20a%20mob%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20photo%20of%20a%20charred%20body%20of%20a%2045-year-old%20woman%20has%20recently%20surfaced%20online%2C%20following%20the%20video%20of%20strip-parade%20horror%20came%20to%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fwomen-were-stripped-raped-set-ablaze-in-manipur-more-cases-surface%2Farticle67106726.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Pastor%20Thianna%20Vaiphei%20Sauntak%20from%20Pheitaiching%20village%20said%20he%20had%20found%20the%20semi-charred%20body%20of%20the%2045-year-old%20mother%20of%20two%20on%20May%207%2C%20a%20day%20after%20a%20large%20mob%20had%20attacked%20the%20village.%20He%20said%20he%20went%20there%20under%20army%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20body%20was%20half%20burnt%2C%20she%20was%20naked.%20The%20body%20was%20taken%20away%20to%20a%20government%20hospital%20in%20Imphal%2C%20we%20do%20not%20know%20where%20it%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sauntak%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalled%20that%20armed%20men%2C%20wearing%20black%20shirts%2C%20had%20descended%20on%20the%20village%20on%20May%206.%20He%20claimed%20that%20Manipur%20Police%20commandos%20had%20accompanied%20the%20mob.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20our%20houses%20were%20torched%2C%20most%20villagers%20were%20able%20to%20flee%20the%20scene.%20The%20woman%2C%20who%20used%20to%20live%20alone%2C%20could%20not%20run%20away%20and%20was%20caught%20by%20the%20mob.%20She%20was%20killed%2C%20her%20body%20was%20mutilated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20a%20zero%20FIR%20was%20registered%20at%20Kangpokpi%20and%20was%20later%20transferred%20to%20Imphal%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20always%20expected%20the%20police%20to%20help%20us%2C%20instead%20they%20fired%20at%20us.%20The%20village%20volunteers%20also%20ran%20away%2C%20the%20woman%20was%20left%20behind.%20It%20is%20a%20horrible%20situation%2C%20I%20have%20never%20experienced%20anything%20like%20this%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20pastor%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20legislators%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkuki-zo-people-hold-rally-for-separate-administration-in-churachandpur%2Farticle67102568.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3Ethe%20Kuki-Zo%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20seven%20from%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20released%20a%20statement%20mentioning%20at%20least%20four%20other%20incidents%20where%20women%20belonging%20to%20their%20community%20were%20either%20raped%20or%20murdered%20since%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690032799000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmanipur-after-strip-parade-horror-more-cases-of-sexual-assault-surface%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20the%20internet%20ban%20in%20the%20state%2C%20a%20number%20of%20instances%20of%20sex%20assault%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20Manipur%20are%20coming%20to%20light.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmanipur-after-strip-parade-horror-more-cases-of-sexual-assault-surface%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Second%20Wife%20Can't%20File%20Cruelty%20Case%20Against%20Husband%3A%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20has%20set%20aside%20the%20conviction%20of%20a%2046-year-old%20man%20under%20Section%20498A%20(married%20woman%20subject%20to%20cruelty)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20as%20the%20complaint%20was%20his%20'second%20wife'%2C%20making%20the%20marriage%20%26quot%3Bnull%20and%20void%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20single%20judge%20bench%20of%20Justice%20S%20Rachaiah%20in%20its%20judgement%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOnce%20PW.1%20(complainant%20woman)%20is%20considered%20as%20the%20second%20wife%20of%20the%20petitioner%2C%20obviously%2C%20the%20complaint%20filed%20against%20the%20petitioner%20for%20the%20offence%20under%20Section%20498-A%20of%20IPC%20ought%20not%20to%20have%20been%20entertained.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20other%20words%2C%20a%20complaint%20filed%20by%20the%20second%20wife%20against%20the%20husband%20and%20her%20in-laws%20is%20not%20maintainable.%20The%20courts%20below%20committed%20an%20error%20in%20applying%20the%20principles%20and%20also%20the%20law%20in%20this%20aspect.%20Therefore%2C%20interference%20by%20this%20court%20in%20exercising%20the%20revisional%20jurisdiction%20is%20justified%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20Criminal%20Revision%20Petition%20filed%20by%20Kantharaju%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Vittavathanahalli%20in%20the%20state's%20Tumakuru%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant%20had%20claimed%20that%20she%20was%20Kantharaju's%20second%20wife%20and%20that%20they%20lived%20together%20for%20five%20years%20and%20had%20a%20son%20together.%20But%20she%20later%20got%20paralysed%20and%20became%20incapacitated.%20Kantharaju%20began%20harassing%20her%20after%20this%20and%20subjected%20her%20to%20cruelty%20and%20mental%20torture%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20against%20him%20and%20the%20Trial%20Court%20in%20Tumakuru%20found%20him%20guilty%20in%20January%202019.%20The%20conviction%20was%20confirmed%20by%20a%20Sessions%20Court%20in%20October%202019.%20Kantharaju%20approached%20the%20High%20Court%20with%20the%20Revision%20Petition%20the%20same%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20set%20aside%20the%20lower%20court%20order%20as%20it%20found%20that%20a%20second%20wife%20was%20not%20entitled%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%20under%20Section%20498A.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20prosecution%20has%20to%20establish%20that%20the%20marriage%20of%20PW.1%20is%20legal%20or%20she%20is%20the%20legally%20wedded%20wife%20of%20the%20petitioner.%20Unless%20it%20is%20established%20that%20she%20is%20the%20legally%20wedded%20wife%20of%20the%20petitioner%2C%20the%20courts%20below%20ought%20to%20have%20acted%20upon%20the%20evidence%20of%20PWs.1%20(complainant%20woman)%20and%202%20(her%20mother)%20that%20PW.1%20was%20the%20second%20wife%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20two%20judgements%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20-%20Shivcharan%20Lal%20Verma%20case%20and%20the%20P%20Sivakumar%20case%2C%20the%20High%20Court%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20ratio%20of%20these%20two%20judgments%20of%20the%20Hon'ble%20Supreme%20Court%20clearly%20indicates%20that%20if%20the%20marriage%20between%20the%20husband%20and%20wife%20ended%20as%20null%20and%20void%2C%20the%20offence%20under%20Section%20498A%20of%20IPC%20cannot%20be%20sustained.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESetting%20aside%20Kantharaju's%20conviction%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAdmittedly%2C%20in%20the%20present%20case%2C%20the%20complainant%20in%20her%20evidence%2C%20PW.2%20being%20the%20mother%20of%20PW.1%20both%20have%20consistently%20deposed%20and%20admitted%20that%2C%20PW.1%20is%20the%20second%20wife%20of%20the%20petitioner.%20Accordingly%2C%20the%20concurrent%20findings%20of%20the%20courts%20below%20in%20recording%20the%20conviction%20require%20to%20be%20set%20aside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690032660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-02%2F7nrvsosc_karnataka-high-court-650_625x300_22_February_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsecond-wife-cannot-file-cruelty-case-against-husband-under-section-498a-karnataka-high-court-4232065%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20has%20set%20aside%20the%20conviction%20of%20a%2046-year-old%20man%20under%20Section%20498A%20(married%20woman%20subject%20to%20cruelty)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20as%20the%20complaint%20was%20his%20'second%20wife'%2C%20making%20the%20marriage%20%26quot%3Bnull%20and%20void%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsecond-wife-cannot-file-cruelty-case-against-husband-under-section-498a-karnataka-high-court-4232065%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsecond-wife-cannot-file-cruelty-case-against-husband-under-section-498a-karnataka-high-court-4232065%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsecond-wife-cannot-file-cruelty-case-against-husband-under-section-498a-karnataka-high-court-4232065%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Pathetic%20Umpiring%5C%22%3A%20Harmanpreet%20Blasts%20Officials%20After%20Bangladesh%20ODI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20livid%20India%20women's%20captain%20Harmanpreet%20Kaur%20did%20not%20mince%20words%20in%20criticising%20the%20umpiring%20during%20the%20tied%20third%20ODI%20against%20Bangladesh%20on%20Saturday%2C%20terming%20it%20%26quot%3Bpathetic%26quot%3B.%20India%20were%20bowled%20out%20for%20225%20in%2049.3%20overs%20after%20Bangladesh%20posted%20their%20highest%20total%20in%20the%2050-over%20format%20against%20India%2C%20scoring%20225%2F4%20batting%20first%20with%20Fargana%20Hoque%20(107)%20recording%20the%20first-ever%20ODI%20century%20for%20her%20country.%20India%20opener%20Smriti%20Mandhana%20scored%2059%20at%20the%20top%20while%20middle-order%20batter%20Harleen%20Deol%20made%2077%2C%20but%20India%20collapsed%20from%20191%20for%20four%20to%20225%20all%20out%2C%20losing%20the%20last%20six%20wickets%20for%20a%20mere%2034%20runs%20and%20had%20to%20settle%20for%20a%20tied%20three-match%20ODI%20series%201-1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20(there%20is)%20a%20lot%20of%20learning%20for%20us%20from%20the%20game.%20Even%20apart%20from%20the%20cricket%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20umpiring%20that%20was%20happening%2C%20we%20were%20very%20surprised.%20The%20next%20time%20we%20come%20to%20Bangladesh%20we%20will%20make%20sure%20we%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20this%20type%20of%20umpiring%20and%20prepare%20ourselves%20accordingly%2C%26quot%3B%20Harmanpreet%20told%20the%20broadcaster%20after%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20last%20pair%20of%20Jemimah%20Rodrigues%20(33%20not%20out)%20and%20Meghna%20Singh%20(6)%20took%20the%20team%20close%20to%20win%2C%20but%20a%20contentious%20caught-behind%20decision%20against%20the%20latter%20seems%20to%20have%20added%20to%20India's%20woes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Jemimah%20and%20Meghna%20looked%20unhappy%20with%20the%20caught-behind%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India%20captain%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20on-field%20umpires%20Muhammad%20Kamruzzaman%20and%20Tanvir%20Ahmed%20--%20both%20locals%20--%20by%20terming%20their%20umpiring%20as%20%26quot%3Bpathetic%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarmanpreet%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20(Bangladesh)%20batted%20really%20well%2C%20batted%20according%20to%20the%20situation.%20They%20were%20taking%20those%20singles%20which%20were%20very%20crucial.%20In%20between%2C%20we%20leaked%20a%20few%20runs%20but%20we%20controlled%20the%20game%20very%20well%20when%20we%20were%20batting%2C%20but%20as%20I%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20some%20pathetic%20umpiring%20was%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20really%20disappointed%20about%20some%20decisions%20given%20by%20the%20umpires%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20India%20captain%2C%20who%20hit%20the%20stumps%20with%20her%20bat%20in%20frustration%20and%20gestured%20towards%20the%20umpire%20when%20she%20was%20adjudged%20out%20leg-before%20for%2014%20off%20Nahida%20Akter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India%20captain%20praised%20Harleen%20Deol%20for%20her%2077%2C%20which%20came%20off%20108%20balls%20with%20nine%20fours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20looked%20very%20promising%20in%20the%20last%20game%2C%20so%20we%20promoted%20her%20to%20bat%20freely%20and%20she%20took%20the%20opportunity%20with%20both%20hands.%20Jemi%20(Jemimah)%20was%20really%20good%20throughout%20the%20innings.%20She%20played%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(It%20was%20a)%20good%20game%2C%20(a)%20lot%20of%20learning%20and%20lastly%20our%20High%20Commission%20from%20India%20is%20also%20there%20and%20I%20hope%20you%20could%20have%20invited%20him%20here%2C%20but%20that%20is%20also%20fine.%20And%20thank%20you%20sir%20for%20com