0voters%20said%20their%20top%20concerns%20were%20the%20economic%20crisis%2C%20unemployment%2C%20political%20problems%20in%20general%2C%20health%20care%C2%A0and%20the%20quality%20of%20available%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpain%20was%20hit%20hard%20by%20the%20coronavirus%20pandemic%20and%20is%20still%20feeling%20its%20effects%3A%20The%20country%20of%2047%20million%20had%20by%20far%20the%20highest%20unemployment%20rate%20in%20the%20EU%20in%20May%2C%20at%2012.7%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20country%20approaches%20Election%20Day%2C%20Sanchez%20has%20tried%20to%20energize%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20base%20by%C2%A0invoking%C2%A0centrist%20voters%E2%80%99%20fears%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20a%20right-wing%20coalition.%20Part%20of%20the%20logic%20in%20calling%20snap%20elections%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20the%20general%20poll%20was%20originally%20set%20for%20much%20later%20this%20year%C2%A0%E2%80%94%C2%A0was%20to%20quickly%20unify%20the%20left%2C%20Encarnacion%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFeijoo%20has%20slammed%20the%20photogenic%2C%20internationally%20popular%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20style%20of%20government%2C%20which%20the%20PP%20dubs%20%E2%80%9CSanchismo.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0The%20conservative%20leader%20has%20accused%20Sanchez%20of%20centering%20the%20campaign%20on%20his%20personality%C2%A0and%20of%20flip-flopping%20on%20important%20issues.%20Sanchez%2C%20Feijoo%20said%20in%20a%20speech%20last%20Friday%2C%20has%20made%20his%20career%20on%20%E2%80%9Cagreeing%20to%20anything%20with%20anyone%20in%20order%20to%20get%20into%20power%20and%20stay%20there%2C%20lying%20about%20important%20issues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight-wing%20leaders%20have%20also%20criticised%20Sanchez%20for%20working%20with%20Catalan%20and%20Basque%20independence%20forces%20to%20get%20certain%20policies%20over%20the%20line.%20He%20also%20pardoned%20nine%20jailed%20Catalonian%20independence%20leaders%20in%202021%2C%20a%20move%20that%20earned%20him%20strong%20rebukes%20from%20PP%20and%20Vox.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESanchez%E2%80%99s%20big%20bet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchez%20has%20staked%20his%20political%20career%20on%20a%20risky%20calculation%3A%20That%20holding%20early%20elections%20will%20help%20crystallise%20support%20behind%20his%20party.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20it%20might%20not%20be%20his%20personal%20performance%20that%20seals%20the%20deal%20either%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20election%20will%20likely%20be%20decided%20by%20how%20the%20supporting%20parties%20perform.%C2%A0The%20polls%20show%20Podemos%2FSumar%20overtaking%20Vox%3B%20if%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20case%20then%20the%20gamble%20would%20pay%20off%2C%E2%80%9D%20Encarnacion%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Sanchez%E2%80%99s%20move%20fails%20and%20the%20PP%20does%20team%20up%20with%20Vox%20for%20a%20national%20governing%20coalition%2C%20the%20junior%20partner%20would%20be%20the%20furthest-right%20force%20in%20the%20Spanish%20government%20since%20the%20end%20of%20the%20fascist%20dictatorship%20of%20Francisco%20Franco%20in%20the%201970s.%20But%2C%20Encarnacion%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CVox%20would%20be%20a%20very%20junior%20partner%20in%20a%20PP-Vox%20coalition.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20EU%20countries%2C%20traditional%20centre-right%20parties%20have%20been%20lambasted%20for%20even%20considering%20breaking%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Ccordon%20sanitaire%E2%80%9D%20between%20more%20mainstream%20parties%20and%20the%20far%20right%3A%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20conservative%20Christian%20Democrats%2C%20for%20example%2C%20have%20faced%20massive%20criticism%20for%20even%20local-%20and%20regional-level%20attempts%20to%20vote%20alongside%20the%20populist%20far-right%20Alternative%20for%20Germany%20party.%20No%20such%20cordon%20sanitaire%20exists%20in%20Spain%2C%20according%20to%20Encarnacion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20PP%20is%20a%20late%201980s%20reinvention%20of%20Alianza%20Popular%2C%20a%20neo-Francoist%20party%20that%20formed%20during%20the%20democratic%20transition%20in%20the%20late%201970s.%20And%20VOX%C2%A0is%20an%20offshoot%20of%20the%20PP%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%20Nationalist-conservative%20Abascal%C2%A0left%20the%20PP%20to%20form%20Vox%2C%20which%20takes%20a%20hard%20line%20on%20Catalonian%20nationalism%20and%C2%A0saw%20its%20support%20surge%20amid%20the%20fallout%20from%20the%20independence%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20opinion%20polls%20hold%20true%20on%20Sunday%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20possible%20that%20no%20one%20party%20emerges%20victorious%20or%20is%20even%20able%20to%20build%20an%20immediate%20coalition.%20Repeat%20elections%20are%20a%20distinct%20possibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhatever%20happens%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20%5BSocialists%5D%20will%20remain%20a%20force%20in%20Spanish%20politics.%20And%20the%20rise%20of%20Vox%20only%20dates%20to%202019%2C%E2%80%9D%20Encarnacion%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20said%2C%20an%20unavoidable%20impression%20would%20be%20the%20rising%20fortunes%20of%20the%20far%20right.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchez%E2%80%99s%20big%20bet%20will%20likely%20have%20repercussions%20that%20reverberate%20throughout%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fspanish-elections-will-sanchezs-political-gamble-pay-off%2Fa-66288935%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftop-stories%2Fs-9097%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flogs1279.xiti.com%2Fhit.xiti%3Fs%3D531599%26s2%3D2%26p%3Dthewire.in%3A%3AVolltexte%3A%3Athewire.in_Volltexte_JS%26di%3D%26an%3D%26ac%3D%26x1%3D1%26x2%3D2%26x5%3Dthewire.in_Volltexte_JS%26x6%3D1%26x8%3Den-VAS-Volltexte-JavaScript-thewire.in-dwde%26x10%3Dthewire.in%3A%3AVolltexte%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publishe