y%2Famp%2Ficy-water-courses-through-italian-streets-after-dramatic-hailstorm-12925407%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%2075%25%20of%20High%20Court%20Judges%20Appointed%20Since%202018%20Are%20from%20Upper%20Castes%3A%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F20150700%2Fimage-598.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThree%20out%20of%20four%20judges%20appointed%20to%20high%20courts%20in%20the%20country%20since%202018%20are%20from%20upper-caste%20communities.%20In%20precise%20terms%2C%20458%20out%20of%20604%20(75.68%25)%20judges%20appointed%20from%202018%20to%20July%2017%20this%20year%20were%20from%20the%20General%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20information%20is%20based%20on%20the%20figures%20disclosed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20by%20Union%20law%20minister%2C%20Arjun%20Meghwal%2C%20on%20Friday%2C%20July%2021.%20Meghwal%20responded%20to%20All%20India%20Majlis-E-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%20MP%2C%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%2C%20who%20sought%20the%20information%20on%20the%20social%20profile%20of%20high%20court%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20figures%20also%20reveal%20that%2018%20(2.98%25)%20and%20nine%20(1.49%25)%20judges%20elevated%20as%20high%20court%20judges%20in%20the%20same%20period%20belonged%20to%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeventy-two%20judges%20(11.92%25)%20from%20the%20OBC%20community%20were%20elevated%20as%20high%20court%20judges%20in%20the%20same%20period%2C%20and%20the%20figure%20for%20judges%20from%20minority%20communities%20stood%20at%2034%20(5.6%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%E2%80%99s%20response%20came%20as%20an%20answer%20to%20Owaisi%E2%80%99s%20question%2C%20which%20sought%20to%20know%20%E2%80%9Cwhether%20it%20is%20a%20fact%20that%2079%25%20judges%20appointed%20in%20High%20Courts%20were%20from%20the%20upper%20castes%20during%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20%E2%80%98indicating%20an%20inequitable%20representation%20of%20backward%20and%20minority%20communities'%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%202011%20Census%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%20account%20for%2016.6%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20while%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20for%208.6%25.%20Minority%20communities%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20represent%2019.3%25%20of%20the%20population.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20no%20count%20of%20OBCs%2C%20as%20caste%20was%20not%20considered%20during%20the%20last%20census.%20If%20one%20were%20to%20go%20by%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%20report%2C%20their%20share%20in%20the%20population%20accounted%20for%2052%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisclosing%20the%20information%2C%20Meghwal%20added%20that%20the%20appointment%20of%20judges%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20High%20Courts%20is%20made%20under%20Articles%20124%2C%20217%2C%20and%20224%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20which%2C%20he%20said%2C%20do%20not%20provide%20for%20reservation%20for%20any%20caste%20or%20class%20of%20persons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20government%20has%20been%20requesting%20the%20Chief%20Justices%20of%20High%20Courts%20that%20while%20sending%20proposals%20for%20the%20appointment%20of%20judges%2C%20due%20consideration%20be%20given%20to%20suitable%20candidates%20belonging%20to%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20OBCs%2C%20minorities%2C%20and%20women%20to%20ensure%20social%20diversity%20in%20the%20appointment%20of%20judges%20in%20High%20Courts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2Fthree-of-four-high-court-judges-upper-castes-dalits-tribals-account-for-less-than-5-1239385.html%5C%22%3Eadded%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20Memorandum%20of%20Procedure%20for%20appointment%20of%20Judges%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20high%20courts%2C%20the%20government%20appoints%20only%20those%20persons%20who%20are%20recommended%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Collegium%2C%20he%20further%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20trying%20to%20gain%20control%20over%20judicial%20appointments%20by%20doing%20away%20with%20the%20Collegium%20System%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20maintained%20that%20in%20the%20three%20decades%20since%20the%20system%20has%20been%20in%20place%2C%20it%20has%20failed%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2Fthree-of-four-high-court-judges-upper-castes-dalits-tribals-account-for-less-than-5-1239385.html%5C%22%3Esocial%20diversity%20in%20the%20higher%20judiciary%2C%20as%20originally%20devised%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Union%20law%20ministry%20told%20a%20parliamentary%20panel%20that%20%E2%80%9Cinequitable%20representation%20of%20backward%20and%20minority%20communities%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20higher%20judiciary%20is%20%E2%80%9Cevident%20from%20the%20fact%E2%80%9D%20that%2079%25%20of%20all%20high%20court%20judges%20appointed%20between%202018%20and%202022%20were%20from%20upper%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690020264000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F20150700%2Fimage-598.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fover-75-of-high-court-judges-appointed-since-2018-are-from-upper-castes-centre%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20proportion%20of%20Dalits%20and%20Tribals%20among%20these%20appointees%20is%20less%20than%205%25%2C%20Union%20law%20ministry%20revealed%20in%20the%20parliament.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fover-75-of-high-court-judges-appointed-since-2018-are-from-upper-castes-centre%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Oppenheimer%20beats%20Barbie%20on%20day%201%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690019483000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102037092%2C