-of-young-people-scour-irish-beach-after-large-bales-of-suspected-cocaine-wash-ashore-12925342%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kudankulam%20Protest%3A%20Court%20Awards%20Seven-Year%20Imprisonment%20to%2018%20Persons%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F13193659%2Fnuclear-protest-pti_0.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20sub-court%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20on%20Friday%2C%20July%2021%20awarded%20seven%20years%20of%20imprisonment%20to%2018%20people%2C%20including%20four%20women%2C%20in%20a%20case%20related%20to%20a%20protest%20against%20the%20Kudankulam%20nuclear%20power%20project.%20A%20penalty%20of%20Rs%20500%20was%20also%20imposed%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20registered%20against%2022%20persons%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20were%20fishermen.%20They%20allegedly%20attacked%20two%20other%20fishermen%20who%20refused%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20protest%20against%20the%20nuclear%20power%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%2018%20persons%20were%20convicted%2C%20three%20persons%20%E2%80%93%20S.P.%20Udayakumar%2C%20Pushparayan%20and%20M.P.%20Jesuraj%20%E2%80%93%20who%20were%20coordinators%20of%20the%20protest%2C%20were%20acquitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThousands%20conducted%20protests%20for%20over%20several%20years%20in%20Idinthakarai%20against%20KKNPP%20%5BKudankulam%20Nuclear%20Power%20Plant%5D.%20More%20than%20300%20police%20cases%20were%20registered%20against%20the%20protesters.%20While%20most%20of%20them%20were%20withdrawn%2C%2063%20are%20pending%20before%20the%20court.%20In%202013%2C%20the%20protesting%20fishermen%20decided%20to%20give%20away%20a%20share%20of%20their%20catch%20to%20manage%20the%20expenses%20of%20the%20protest%2C%20but%20S.%20Elango%20and%20R.%20Brighten%20allegedly%20refused%20to%20budge.%20After%20being%20attacked%20by%20the%20convicts%2C%20the%20duo%20filed%20separate%20complaints%20with%20the%20police%20who%20registered%20a%20case%20against%2022%20persons%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fstates%2Ftamil-nadu%2F2023%2Fjul%2F22%2F18-kudankulam-protesters-awarded-seven-year-jail-term-2597301.html%5C%22%3Esources%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIdinthakarai%20is%20a%20village%20close%20to%20the%20Kudankulam%20nuclear%20power%20plant%20which%20became%20the%20protest%E2%80%99s%20ground%20zero.%20Here%2C%20Udaykumar%20and%20others%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthoothukudi-isnt-alone-tamil-nadu-has-been-rising-in-protest-for-decades%5C%22%3Eorganised%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20hunger%20strike%20in%20shifts%2C%20observed%20for%20over%20500%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Udaykumar%20urged%20the%20state%20government%20to%20withdraw%20all%20the%20cases%20registered%20against%20the%20people%20who%20protested%20against%20the%20nuclear%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaying%20that%20the%20cases%20are%20affecting%20the%20livelihood%20of%20the%20villagers%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20state%20government%20should%20either%20withdraw%20the%20cases%20or%20should%20at%20least%20expedite%20the%20legal%20proceedings.%20Still%2C%20the%20names%20of%20many%20people%20feature%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98wanted%20list%E2%80%99.%20The%20youngsters%2C%20searching%20for%20jobs%2C%20are%20the%20most%20affected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20stated%20by%20Minister%20for%20Electricity%20V.%20Senthil%20Balaji%2C%20the%20state%20government%20should%20hear%20the%20public%20opinion%20on%20the%20construction%20of%20Unit%205%20and%206%20in%20Kudankulam%20and%20take%20steps%20to%20stop%20the%20construction%20works.%20The%20people%20of%20Kudankulam%20are%20against%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20power%20plant.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690012161000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F13193659%2Fnuclear-p