anslate%20what%20they%20said%20but%20we%20got%20a%20sense%20of%20what%20they%20wanted%20in%20a%20playground%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20play%20elements%20you%20see%20on%20playgrounds%20built%20by%20Anthill%20like%20octopus%2C%20elephants%20or%20horses%20came%20from%20children.%20Other%20children%20wanted%20a%20rocket%20in%20their%20playground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20tried%20to%20incorporate%20some%20of%20those%20major%20structural%20designs%2C%20but%20also%20keep%20activities%20in%20mind%20when%20we%20were%20designing%20those%20final%20elements.%20It%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20iterations.%20Not%20all%20of%20our%20design%20elements%20became%20successful%20in%20the%20first%20go%2C%20but%20we%20seek%20to%20ensure%20a%20constant%20feedback%20loop%20that%20happened.%20We%20still%20engage%20in%20these%20processes%2C%20but%20today%20we%20have%20around%20100%20different%20designs%20in%20our%20design%20library%20although%20we%20still%20take%20requests%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Rai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20we%E2%80%99re%20operating%20at%20a%20much%20larger%20scale%20today%2C%20we%20have%20this%20written%20site%20survey%20form%20that%20either%20we%20fill%20when%20we%20visit%20a%20site%20or%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20local%20community%20or%20a%20teacher%20who%20fills%20it%20out%20for%20us.%20That%20basically%20captures%20what%20children%20need%20and%20if%20there%20is%20anything%20in%20specific%20that%20like%20that%20particular%20community%20or%20school%20wants%20to%20do%2C%20we%20look%20at%20our%20design%20library%20and%20see%20what%20fits%20well%20into%20this%20playground.%20We%20try%20to%20leave%20some%20space%20for%20designing%20new%20elements%20as%20well%20because%20we%20want%20to%20give%20some%20unique%20touch%20to%20most%20of%20our%20playgrounds%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20756px)%20100vw%2C%20756px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPretend-play-elements-Elephant-1689861074.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22756%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Innovative%20playgrounds%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPretend-play-elements-Elephant-1689861074.jpg%20756w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPretend-play-elements-Elephant-1689861074-281x300.jpg%20281w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPretend-play-elements-Elephant-1689861074-500x534.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPretend-play-elements-Elephant-1689861074-150x160.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324647%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22807%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPretend%20Play%20Element%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20an%20elephant.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20do%20they%20make%20these%20playgrounds%20inclusive%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20stated%20earlier%2C%20there%20are%20playgrounds%20with%20elements%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20come%20from%20their%20design%20library.%20After%20all%2C%20they%20have%20to%20cater%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20children%2C%20including%20those%20living%20with%20disabilities.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202021%2C%20they%20built%20a%20playground%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Sankalp%20Learning%20Centre%20in%20Chennai%20for%20children%20with%20autism%20and%20intellectual%20disabilities.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20playground%20designed%20for%20autistic%20children%20in%20our%20library.%20For%20projects%20like%20these%2C%20we%20spent%20time%20with%20the%20children%2C%20understanding%20what%20works%20for%20them%2C%20what%20will%20help%20in%20their%20therapy%20and%20use%20tactile%20sensors%20in%20the%20playgrounds%20which%20might%20help%20them.%20In%20terms%20of%20design%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20tactile.%20We%20wanted%20children%20to%20just%20feel%20different%20kinds%20of%20senses%20and%20build%20something%20that%20they%20can%20touch%20with%20their%20hands%20and%20also%20play%20with%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rai.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20included%20a%20xylophone%20for%20sensory%20stimulation%2C%20parallel%20pay%20bars%20for%20wrist%20and%20finger%20movements%2C%20a%20seesaw%20to%20encourage%20balance%20and%20body%20coordination%2C%20and%20a%20low%20height%20climber%20to%20ensure%20muscular%20movement%20and%20safety%20for%20the%20children%20while%20at%20play%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERai%20admits%20that%20Anthill%E2%80%99s%20playgrounds%20aren%E2%80%99t%20completely%20inclusive%20yet%2C%20but%20they%20try%20to%20make%20them%20accessible.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20incorporating%20play%20elements%20used%20in%20playgrounds%20built%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F293875%2Fworlds-first-braille-literacy-award-winning-device-annie-innovation-for-blind-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evisually-impaired%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20all%20our%20playgrounds.%20For%20example%2C%20we%20have%20introduced%20sound%20elements%20like%20xylophone%20or%20bells%20in%20all%20our%20playgrounds.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20playgrounds%20inclusive%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20833px)%20100vw%2C%20833px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-for-the-blind-india-1689861447.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Playgrounds%20for%20blind%20children%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22833%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-for-the-blind-india-1689861447.jpg%20833w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-for-the-blind-india-1689861447-300x297.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-for-the-blind-india-1689861447-500x496.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-for-the-blind-india-1689861447-150x149.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-for-the-blind-india-1689861447-768x762.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-for-the-blind-india-1689861447-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324649%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22826%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAnthill%20recently%20built%20a%20playground%20for%20the%20Calcutta%20Blind%20School.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20%E2%80%98community%20champions%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Anthill%20has%20learnt%20over%20the%20years%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20better%20to%20involve%20the%20community%20early%20in%20the%20process%20right%20from%20the%20site%20selection%20to%20what%20they%20are%20designing.%20When%20they%20involve%20the%20community%20from%20the%20beginning%2C%20they%20take%20greater%20ownership%20of%20the%20playgrounds.%20Typically%2C%20what%20Anthill%20does%20is%20build%20a%20playground%2C%20and%20hands%20it%20over%20to%20the%20community%20to%20take%20care%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20do%20they%20obtain%20community%20buy-in%20for%20these%20playgrounds%3F%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20work%20in%20a%20new%20geography%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20always%20a%20local%20organisation%20or%20NGO%20who%20might%20have%20been%20working%20in%20these%20communities%20for%20years%20and%20already%20have%20that%20relationship%20built%20with%20them.%20When%20they%20bring%20us%20in%2C%20there%20is%20that%20sense%20of%20respect%20and%20trust%20already%20established%20when%20we%20go%20in.%20On%20our%20end%2C%20we%20also%20spend%20time%20with%20people%20explaining%20to%20them%20what%20structure%20is%20going%20to%20come%20up%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20maintain%20costs%2C%20Anthill%20largely%20procures%20materials%20locally%20and%20employs%20local%20labour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGiven%20the%20elements%20that%20we%E2%80%99ve%20designed%20are%20simple%20and%20basic%20like%20tires%20and%20metal%20drums%2C%20and%20engage%20in%20recycling%20and%20upcycling%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20make%20sense%20to%20transport%20things%20from%20Bengaluru%20to%20Tripura.%20We%20procure%20materials%20locally%20because%20it%20saves%20cost%2C%20available%20locally.%20Where%20it%20becomes%20challenging%20is%20to%20ensure%20the%20quality%20that%20we%20want%20in%20these%20elements%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20overcome%20these%20concerns%2C%20we%20have%20a%20set%20of%20vendors%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20we%20transport%20these%20joineries%20from%20one%20central%20hub%20to%20wherever%20we%20are%20building%20playgrounds.%20Elements%20like%20tires%20and%20metal%2C%20we%20procure%20locally%20because%20those%20are%20like%20the%20bigger%20bulk%20of%20what%20we%20kind%20of%20use%20to%20design%20these%20playgrounds.%20Given%20we%20have%20now%20built%20playgrounds%20in%2022%20different%20states%2C%20we%20have%20identified%20vendors%20and%20all%20of%20these%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20as%20stated%20earlier%2C%C2%A0%20Anthill%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20take%20ownership%20of%20the%20playgrounds%20they%20build.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20just%20facilitators%20who%20are%20enabling%20the%20local%20community%20or%20the%20school%20to%20build%20a%20playground.%20We%20bring%20in%20funding%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20corporation%20and%20provide%20our%20expertise%20in%20how%20to%20construct%20the%20playground.%20But%20after%20those%20six%20days%20of%20intervention%2C%20our%20major%20role%20is%20complete%20in%20building%20the%20playground%20and%20we%20hand%20it%20over%20to%20the%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20this%20handover%20period%20is%20over%20one%20or%20three%20months%2C%20it%20varies%20based%20on%20where%20the%20playground%20is%20located.%20They%20often%20complete%20building%20the%20playground%20in%20six%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20last%20day%2C%20we%20do%20a%20quality%20check%20with%20the%20corporate%20who%E2%80%99s%20funding%20the%20project%20and%20the%20local%20headmaster%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20playground%20we%E2%80%99ve%20constructed%20meets%20all%20the%20basic%20quality%20measures.%20And%20then%20we%20proceed%20towards%20our%20adoption%20plan.%20We%20identify%20one%20community%20champion.%20It%20could%20be%20anyone%20from%20a%20headmaster%20to%20a%20teacher%20or%20an%20alumni%20of%20that%20school%2C%20who%20was%20involved%20in%20building%20that%20playground%20and%20is%20happy%20to%20volunteer%20their%20time.%20We%20maintain%20correspondence%20with%20them.%20After%20one%20month%2C%20we%20contact%20them%20to%20do%20a%20basic%20check%20on%20how%20children%20are%20playing%20in%20these%20playgrounds.%20We%20have%20a%20questionnaire%20that%20they%20answer%20to%20help%20us%20assess%20the%20impact%20of%20this%20playground.%20We%20get%20both%20quantitative%20and%20qualitative%20feedback%20and%20whenever%20we%E2%80%99re%20building%20a%20new%20play%20element%2C%20we%20receive%20some%20extra%20feedback%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201300px)%20100vw%2C%201300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-7-1689861524.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Innovative%20playgrounds%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-7-1689861524.jpg%201300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-7-1689861524-300x141.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-7-1689861524-500x235.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-7-1689861524-768x360.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-7-1689861524-150x70.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324650%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22610%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EInnovative%20play%20spaces.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Our%20playgrounds%20are%20like%20IKEA%20blocks%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20handing%20their%20playgrounds%20over%20to%20communities%2C%20once%20a%20year%20(or%20once%20in%20two%20years)%20Anthill%20organises%20a%20drive%20where%20their%20team%20travels%20and%20conducts%20checks%20to%20ascertain%20the%20state%20of%20our%20older%20playgrounds.%20Making%20matters%20easier%2C%20their%20playgrounds%20are%20low-maintenance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20our%20playgrounds%20are%20DIY%2C%20we%20do%20not%20refabricate%20(play%20elements%20like)%20a%20conventional%20merry%20go%20round.%20If%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20screw%20coming%20loose%2C%20you%20have%20to%20replace%20the%20merry%20go%20round%20entirely.%20Our%20playgrounds%20are%20like%20IKEA%20blocks.%20You%20can%20fix%20them%2C%20take%20them%20off%20when%20you%20want%20and%20put%20them%20in%20another%20place%20held%20together%20by%20nuts%20and%20bolts%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Rai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20facilitate%20play%20for%20young%20children%2C%20Anthill%20Creations%20has%20come%20up%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20innovations%20to%20facilitate%20greater%20inclusivity%20and%20work%20within%20the%20confines%20of%20different%20circumstances.%20For%20example%2C%20they%20came%20up%20with%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20Play%20Library.%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20we%20used%20smaller%20tires%20to%20create%20seating%20spaces%20in%20a%20more%20interesting%20way%20where%20the%20entire%20space%20felt%20very%20inviting%20for%20children%20to%20play.%20We%20had%20basically%20converted%20a%20library%20into%20a%20play%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Rai.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20one%20of%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20favourite%20innovations%20in%20recent%20years%20is%20this%20concept%20called%20%E2%80%98Playground%20on%20Wheels%E2%80%99%20which%20Anthill%20has%20developed.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20this%20idea%20honestly%20came%20when%20we%20were%20going%20around%20finding%20spaces%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20Bengaluru%20on%20where%20we%20can%20build%20these%20playgrounds%20for%20schools%20that%20contained%20three%20or%20four%20storeys%20and%20nothing%20else%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201514px)%20100vw%2C%201514px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPlaygrounds-Anthill-123-1689861675.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221514%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Building%20innovative%20playgrounds%20for%20children%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPlaygrounds-Anthill-123-1689861675.jpg%201514w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPlaygrounds-Anthill-123-1689861675-300x137.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPlaygrounds-Anthill-123-1689861675-500x229.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPlaygrounds-Anthill-123-1689861675-768x351.jpg%2