he-2-1689772494.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sold%20in%20liquid%20as%20well%20as%20powder%20form%2C%20these%20products%20are%20priced%20between%20Rs%20250%20and%20Rs%20400.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-2-1689772494.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-2-1689772494-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-2-1689772494-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-2-1689772494-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-2-1689772494-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324378%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESold%20in%20liquid%20as%20well%20as%20powder%20form%2C%20these%20products%20are%20priced%20between%20Rs%20250%20and%20Rs%20400.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20the%20carbon%20component%20should%20be%20at%20least%2018%20parts%20as%20compared%20to%20one%20part%20of%20nitrogen%20in%20the%20soil.%20But%20with%20chemicals%2C%20it%20is%20the%20other%20way%20around.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20farmers%20use%20chemical%20fertilisers%20like%20urea%2C%20the%20nitrogen%20increases%20thereby%20decreasing%20the%20carbon%20content.%20Bio%20alternatives%20help%20balance%20this%20with%20the%20help%20of%20organic%20matter%20compost%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20researcher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReduces%20one-third%20of%20expenses%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESangita%20says%20that%20bio%20alternatives%20also%20save%20one-third%20costs%20of%20farmers%20as%20compared%20to%20chemical%20fertilisers.%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20typically%20use%20two%20to%20three%20bags%20of%2050%20kg%20each%20of%20chemical%20fertilisers%20in%20one%20acre%2