%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-2-1689772529.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-2-1689772529-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-2-1689772529-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-2-1689772529-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-2-1689772529-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324380%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EApart%20from%20their%20regular%20syllabus%2C%20the%20children%20also%20get%20to%20do%20activities%20such%20as%20gardening%2C%20painting%20and%20dancing.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Portia%20Putatunda%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Kaza%20was%20a%20tourist%20hub%2C%20Portia%20was%20unable%20to%20find%20a%20reasonably%20priced%20place%20to%20set%20up%20a%20small%20school%20and%20a%20library.%20%E2%80%9CI%20also%20wanted%20to%20set%20up%20a%20dormitory%20and%20a%20kitchen%20for%20children%20who%20do%20not%20have%20a%20home%20to%20go%20to.%20I%20was%20running%20out%20of%20money%20and%20needed%20a%20cheaper%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20when%20she%20got%20to%20know%20about%20a%20place%20in%20Komic%20which%20was%20up%20for%20rent%20at%20a%20very%20low%20price.%20%E2%80%9CRenting%20the%20place%20is%20Komic%20seemed%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do.%20This%20way%20I%20would%20be%20able%20to%20reach%20the%20children%20living%20in%20the%20remotest%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20she%20moved%20to%20Komic%20and%20rented%20the%20place%20to%20start%20a%20free%20boarding%20school%20under%20her%20foundation%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20Planet%20Spiti%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5