s.%20She%20helps%20not%20only%20beloved%20pets%20but%20also%20injured%20wildlife%20like%20jackals%2C%20birds%2C%20and%20snakes.%20Her%20dedication%20to%20treating%20their%20ailments%20is%20unwavering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20her%20daily%20routine%2C%20the%2032-year-old%20sometimes%20experiences%20unique%20days%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F58923%2Fforest-department-karnataka-frontline-staff-incentive%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKarnataka%20Forest%20Department%20%3C%2Fa%3Econtacts%20her%20for%20rescue%20missions.%20She%20helps%20ensure%20that%20the%20wild%20cats%20of%20Karnataka%20are%20safely%20returned%20to%20their%20natural%20habitat%20in%20healthy%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20about%20just%20work%20for%20me%20but%20also%20the%20love%20and%20passion%20I%20have%20for%20these%20animals.%20Humans%20have%20encroached%20on%20their%20lives%2C%20not%20the%20other%20way%20around.%20While%20the%20job%20comes%20with%20a%20set%20of%20risks%2C%20my%20main%20agenda%20is%20always%20to%20get%20the%20animal%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAlways%20an%20animal%20lover%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Meghana%20felt%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306700%2Fgrass-man-of-india-creates-grasslands-habiats-for-tigers-cheetahs-across-india-dr-gajanan-muratkar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaffinity%20for%20the%20wild%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20a%20very%20young%20age.%20She%20always%20loved%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20a%20police%20officer%2C%20and%20we%20moved%20around%20a%20lot%20because%20of%20his%20transferable%20job.%20This%20led%20me%20to%20be%20exposed%20to%20wildlife%20around%20the%20places%20I%20have%20lived.%20Later%20on%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Bengaluru%20to%20do%20my%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20Wildlife%20Sciences%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGrowing%20up%20in%20an%20animal-loving%20family%2C%20I%20was%20constantly%20surrounded%20by%20animals.%20This%20upbringing%20made%20me%20realise%20that%20my%20future%20would%20be%20closely%20connected%20to%20the%20world%20of%20animals.%20Although%20I%20did%20not%20know%20that%20I%20would%20be%20led%20on%20to%20this%20very%20path%20I%E2%80%99m%20on%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20is%20currently%20a%20pet%20parent%20to%20two%20dogs%20and%20a%20few%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-3-1689226283.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meghana%20was%20an%20animal%20lover%20from%20a%20very%20young%20age%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-3-1689226283.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-3-1689226283-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-3-1689226283-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-3-1689226283-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-3-1689226283-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323634%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMeghana%20has%20treated%20a%20plethora%20of%20animals%20including%20snakes%2C%20birds%2C%20jackals%20and%20leopards.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Meghana%20Pemmaiah%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20why%20she%20decided%20to%20get%20into%20rescuing%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20during%20my%20masters%20that%20I%20got%20to%20know%20that%20wildlife%20veterinarian%20was%20a%20thing.%20I%20would%20watch%20people%20on%20NatGeo%20on%20rescue%20missions%20and%20it%20would%20always%20thrill%20me.%20I%20was%20always%20looking%20for%20the%20right%20opportunity%20which%20I%20got%20recently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20her%20degree%2C%20she%20joined%20a%20rescue%20company%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20started%20working%20as%20a%20veterinarian.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202022%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Mangaluru%20with%20my%20husband%20who%20had%20a%20clinic%20there.%20He%20was%20helping%20out%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20forest%20department%2C%20which%20gave%20me%20the%20perfect%20opportunity%20to%20get%20into%20onfield%20rescuing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20nearly%20two%20years%20since%20Meghana%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F122995%2Ffed-delays-26-year-old-creates-app-helps-rescue-animals-real-time%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erescuing%20wild%20animals.%3C%2Fa%3E%20She%20has%20assisted%20the%20forest%20department%20on%20several%20missions%20and%20has%20rescued%20eight%20leopards%2C%20bringing%20them%20home%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EJumping%20in%20wells%20%26amp%3B%20climbing%20building%20is%20a%20routine%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20duty%20call%20for%2024%20hours%2C%20it%20is%20the%20passion%20for%20wildlife%20that%20keeps%20the%20veterinarian%20going.%20She%20has%20been%20in%20rescue%20missions%20which%20entail%20risks%20for%20both%20her%20and%20the%20animal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20go%20on%20a%20mission%2C%20the%20animal%20is%20always%20my%20top%20priority.%20Leopards%20are%20frequently%20the%20ones%20we%20rescue%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20they%20are%20just%20as%20afr