y%20flavourful%20and%20aromatic%2C%20compared%20to%20Hyderabadi%2C%20Muradabadi%2C%20and%20southern%20biryanis.%20Others%20use%20a%20lot%20of%20spices%20and%20ghee.%20We%20feel%20full%20even%20after%20eating%20one%20or%20two%20%3Cem%3Elukma%20%3C%2Fem%3E(mouthfuls).%20There%20is%20a%20class%20in%20Awadh%20food!%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20unique%20species%20and%20cooking%20methods%20she%20uses%20to%20cook%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261268%2Fbiryani-map-of-india-taste-the-history-find-your-favourite-among-28-versions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKolkata%20biryani%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Manzilat%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20I%20prepare%20%3Cem%3Ekorma%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20I%20add%20as%20a%20layer%20in%20the%20utensil.%20After%20this%2C%20I%20add%20a%20layer%20of%20boiled%20potatoes%20savoured%20with%20ghee%2C%20salt%2C%20and%20spices.%20Lastly%2C%20I%20add%20a%20layer%20of%20boiled%20rice%20and%20add%20the%20flavouring%20of%20ghee%20and%20saffron.%20When%20you%20cook%20in%20logs%20and%20%3Cem%3Ematka%3C%2Fem%3Es%20(clay%20utensils)%2C%20it%20gives%20a%20smoky%20flavour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20cook%20biryani%20with%20regular%20spices%20like%20%3Cem%3Ekebab%20chini%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20nutmeg%2C%20%3Cem%3Eshah%20jeera%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20mace%2C%20cardamom%2C%20and%20clove.%20In%20some%20Awadhi%20delicacies%2C%20I%20use%20specialised%20Awadhi%20spices%20and%20herbs%20like%20%3Cem%3Epaan%20ki%20jad%2C%20khas%20ki%20jad%2C%20patthar%20ke%20phool%20%3C%2Fem%3E(herbs).%20They%20are%20more%20aromatic.%20The%20only%20secret%20I%20have%20is%20the%20proportion%20of%20spices%20to%20be%20used%2C%20it%20makes%20a%20lot%20of%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20the%20biryanis%2C%20Manzilat%E2%80%99s%20menu%20offers%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20delicacies%20including%20Lakhnawai%20Mutton%20Yakhni%20Pulao%2C%20Chicken%20Nawabi%20Chaanp%2C%20Ulta%20Tawa%20Paratha%2C%20Fish%20Chatpata%20Handi%20Kabab%2C%20Chicken%20Lazeez%20Shami%20Kabab%2C%20and%20Shahi%20Badam%20Firni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCmf-K96hQC_%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCmf-K96hQC_%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCmf-K96hQC_%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Kolkata%20Food%20Lovers%20(%40kolkatafoodlovers)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELearnt%20cooking%20through%20letters%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManzilat%20recalls%20that%20when%20she%20started%20cooking%20at%20the%20age%20of%2010%2C%20she%20was%20not%20interested%20at%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20living%20with%20my%20father%20in%20Aligarh.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20ordering%20food%20from%20outside%20was%20not%20as%20relevant%20as%20it%20is%20t